<i>determiner</i>: 단적 [단쩍] <i>noun</i>: 단도직입적 [단도지깁쩍] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>determiner</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단적 [단쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>straightforward; point-blank</dd><br>
<dd>분명하고 직접적인.</dd><br>
<dd>Clear and direct.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단도직입적 [단도지깁쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>point-blank; straightforward; speaking without preamble</dd><br>
<dd>쓸데없는 말은 빼고 곧바로 중요한 말을 하는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of saying something important in a straightforward way, without beating about the bush.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>